    <title>v4.36.0</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;README typos fixes  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/2bb3f89e8c3e1f683aa9d3268a82dc8e309b2661/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/2bb3f89e8c3e1f683aa9d3268a82dc8e309b2661&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;2bb3f89&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;updated basic example to showcase content HTML escaping  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/1d488c765ef4abe78064de8ef820c5bf45969292/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/1d488c765ef4abe78064de8ef820c5bf45969292&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;1d488c7&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;fixes &lt;a class=&quot;issue-link js-issue-link&quot; data-error-text=&quot;Failed to load title&quot; data-id=&quot;2662240678&quot; data-permission-text=&quot;Title is private&quot; data-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1411&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;issue&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;/yairEO/tagify/issues/1411/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1411&quot;&gt;#1411&lt;/a&gt; - Fix XSS vulnerability in tag content rendering  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/097451e54f4536eb8415ecfa234cacde719789bc/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/097451e54f4536eb8415ecfa234cacde719789bc&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;097451e&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refactor code formatting in index.html to improve readability and consistency; update class attributes for syntax highlighting and escape HTML entities in JavaScript snippets.  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/bb0a7f17334b731fa97d3f53a9bad762279a8cbc/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/bb0a7f17334b731fa97d3f53a9bad762279a8cbc&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;bb0a7f1&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Prism.js and CSS theme versions; adjust code block formatting in section.njk to escape injected JS content so strings won&#39;t suddenly become HTML tags. this also solves &lt;a class=&quot;issue-link js-issue-link&quot; data-error-text=&quot;Failed to load title&quot; data-id=&quot;2870751478&quot; data-permission-text=&quot;Title is private&quot; data-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1439&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;issue&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;/yairEO/tagify/issues/1439/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1439&quot;&gt;#1439&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/611cda344573d2663237a97dda0b28f15f8bd73e/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/611cda344573d2663237a97dda0b28f15f8bd73e&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;611cda3&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add watchHomepage task to gulpfile for monitoring homepage changes  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/b2b46bb0426d5e5ed05d3bffbc1a49f619862e2a/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/b2b46bb0426d5e5ed05d3bffbc1a49f619862e2a&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;b2b46bb&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;updated packages &amp;amp; browserlist  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/1de456e82a882a7f21bce4dd5501cad26e963419/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/1de456e82a882a7f21bce4dd5501cad26e963419&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;1de456e&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;fixes &lt;a class=&quot;issue-link js-issue-link&quot; data-error-text=&quot;Failed to load title&quot; data-id=&quot;3781193922&quot; data-permission-text=&quot;Title is private&quot; data-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1486&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;issue&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;/yairEO/tagify/issues/1486/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1486&quot;&gt;#1486&lt;/a&gt; - Mix mode: allow pasted content  to be converted into a tags (if exists in the whitelist)  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/733bb7d132f864e224decde4f8e3a5d7a949d6e4/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/733bb7d132f864e224decde4f8e3a5d7a949d6e4&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;733bb7d&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;fixes &lt;a class=&quot;issue-link js-issue-link&quot; data-error-text=&quot;Failed to load title&quot; data-id=&quot;3631658350&quot; data-permission-text=&quot;Title is private&quot; data-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1482&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;issue&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;/yairEO/tagify/issues/1482/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/issues/1482&quot;&gt;#1482&lt;/a&gt; - Backspace key does not remove tag in mix-mode  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/679cec126390130cb572e6ed88e81591eee9b813/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/679cec126390130cb572e6ed88e81591eee9b813&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;679cec1&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;added .cursor files  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/bb17daf7a2e386c2d78063cd1469cf46256d7f6c/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/bb17daf7a2e386c2d78063cd1469cf46256d7f6c&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;bb17daf&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;added to gitignore  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/e2a745146179b2dee3ba614742f6bfec1848f0da/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/e2a745146179b2dee3ba614742f6bfec1848f0da&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;e2a7451&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CSS: Correct capitalization of &lt;code&gt;translateX&lt;/code&gt;  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/5a65c207ffa68363a22d988ca190e48ea6239776/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/5a65c207ffa68363a22d988ca190e48ea6239776&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;5a65c20&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update README.md  &lt;a class=&quot;commit-link&quot; data-hovercard-type=&quot;commit&quot; data-hovercard-url=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/f5f0006083471556f1a5d06e7c65a1aeedfe0bdb/hovercard&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/commit/f5f0006083471556f1a5d06e7c65a1aeedfe0bdb&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;f5f0006&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
